A group of men driving a light grey Volkswagen Polo were caught on CCTV attempting to hijack a black Porsche in Johannesburg.   The men were seen stopping behind the Porsche at one of Hyde Park Corner’s parking exits. Two men alighted from the vehicle wielding firearms. They attempted to open the Porsche but its owner quickly drives out of the parking lot. The men were then seen following the Porsche. It was not clear what happened next‚ but the men reappear and are seen running toward their getaway car. – TimesLIVE